<div class="container benefits">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <h1>Do you have what it takes?</h1>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
        <div class="icon col-xs-2">
          <i class="fa fa-life-ring"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-text col-xs-10">
          <h2>Responsibility</h2>
          <p>You take ownership in the development of Seal's mobile apps. (IOS and Android). You are proactive and eager to learn new technologies. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
        <div class="icon col-xs-2">
          <i class="fa fa-users"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-text col-xs-10">
          <h2>Team Player</h2>
          <p>You work closely with our development team.  You manage additional freelance developers. You can communicate fluently in Dutch & English. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
        <div class="icon col-xs-2">
          <i class="fa fa-code"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-text col-xs-10">
          <h2>Mobile Ninja</h2>
          <p>You have a thorough knowledge of Objective-C, Swift, Java for Android (Hybrid developments). You have experience with API development. (Knowledge of Ruby on Rails is a plus) You develop, maintain and document our code and platforms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
        <div class="icon col-xs-2">
          <i class="fa fa-user-plus"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-text col-xs-10">
          <h2>Experienced</h2>
          <p> You have a minimum 3 years of work experience in a similar position in a professional environment.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="grey-bg">
  <div class="container offer">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12">
        <h1>What's in it for you?</h1>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
          <div class="icon col-xs-2">
            <i class="fa fa-btc"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-text col-xs-10">
            <h2>Competitive Salary</h2>
            <p>If you pay peanuts, you get monkeys.  We go for quality developers, with according benefits.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
          <div class="icon col-xs-2">
            <i class="fa fa-briefcase"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-text col-xs-10">
            <h2>Complete Toolbox</h2>
            <p>We provide you all the tools, to make your work as comfortable and efficient as possible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
          <div class="icon col-xs-2">
            <i class="fa fa-book"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-text col-xs-10">
            <h2>Continuous Learning</h2>
            <p>To keep improving your skills, you can attend conferences and receive additional recourses and courses.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
          <div class="icon col-xs-2">
            <i class="fa fa-space-shuttle"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-text col-xs-10">
            <h2>Dynamic Team</h2>
            <p> You will be part of a young and dynamic team.  Each team member has his speciality, from digital marketing to economics.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container mail-us">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <h1>Seal Your Deal!</h1>
      <p>If you like what's written up here, please send us your brief description, portfolio & cv to martijn@seal-jobs.com!</p>
      <p>We would love you to start as soon as possible.</p>
      <%= mail_to "martijn@seal-jobs.com", subject: "Mobile developer application" do %>
        <button class="btn btn-primary" id="mail"> martijn@seal-jobs.com </button>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

